Do widget blocks not work in Custom Modules on Website Pages?

Using the code below, the text renders in the page editor, but I can't click to edit the text module and the module doesn't appear in the "Edit modules" pane either.

```
{% widget_block rich_text "test" overrideable=True, label='Text' %}
   {% widget_attribute "html" %}
      &lt;h2&gt;Title&lt;/h2&gt;
      &lt;p&gt;Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Vivamus vel consectetur ipsum, in hendrerit nunc. Etiam euismod ut ligula nec vulputate. Suspendisse potenti.&lt;/p&gt;
   {% end_widget_attribute %}
{% end_widget_block %}
```
I've used widget blocks successfully in Custom Modules in emails before, so it puzzles me that I can't get it to work on Website Pages as well.
